{
  "texts": [
    "Research field: RobotReviewer/RobotSearch and ExaCT focus on the medical field, whereas Dextr covers environmental health science.",
    "In contrast, Iris.ai can be employed across various research domains.",
    "(Nasar et al. 2021) to extract various types of information from the relevant articles.",
    "Specifically, ExaCT identifies RCT entities based on the CONSORT statement (Moher et al. 2001).",
    "It returns the top five supporting sentences for each extracted RCT entity, ranked according to relevance."
  ]
}